volume.name: Hopalong Cassidy and the Five Men of Evil

description:
The Arrival begins the Endtime story. The apocalypse is coming and our only hope for survival is Death himself.

So it is that Jack Kurgan, an immortal and agent of Death, has returned to human form. His mission: to locate Sarah and Cole Ramsey, two lost souls who are being drawn deeper into the events that are destined to bring about the end of the world. Jack finds himself getting closer, but time is running out. The price of his failure will be the end of humanity.
name: Book One: The Arrival

description: The Joker, Lex Luthor, Black Manta, Bane, Black Adam, Ras Al Ghul, General Zod, Clayface, Sinestro, Catwoman, Cheetah and many more of the worst villains in the DC Universe star in this action-packed collection of stories from ACTION COMICS ANNUAL #10, BATMAN #244, 614, BATMAN VILLAINS SECRET FILES #1, BLACK ADAM #6, GREEN LANTERN CORPS #14, SOLO #1, SUPERMAN: LEX 2000, WONDER WOMAN #214, COUNTDOWN TO INFINITE CRISIS #1 and the backup stories from COUNTDOWN #2, 6-11, 14-16, 19, 27, 29, 33-34 and 36-37!
name: TPB

volume.name: Necessary Evil: The Villains of the DC Universe

description: Batman and Robin are in a scramble and Egghead is doing the cooking! Hovering high above Gotham City, the hard-boiled criminal is about to drop the Dynamic Duo to their doom. It's anything but over easy for our heroes.
name: The Hatter Takes the Crown

description: Amelia questions The Magistrates use of her time as The Protector. Are her missions all for the greater good, or does he have a hidden agenda? Meanwhile, The Omega Company get the feeling there's something just over the horizon... but it's not what they think!
name: Issue #4

volume.name: Amelia Cole and the Hidden War

description: Arden faces the truth of her situation at Kent United, while Colin plans for the repercussions of Marcus' actions, and First of Cornwall and its allies make their move against the Tricksters.
The final chapter leaves Zak Raven with choices about the island and how his life has changed from his HIV status. His life will never be the same again.
DC Comics Digital Sneak Peeks for 9/4/13.

In this volume of the New York Times bestselling survival horror, Rick and his band of survivors work to build a larger network of thriving communities. But Negan and his Saviors prove to be a larger threat than they could have imagined. Crossing them will lead to THE WALKING DEAD's most harrowing story since the Governor's reign of terror. Collects issues #97-108.
name: Book Nine

description: For years, the Marvel Universe has lived in fear that the artificial intelligence known as Ultron would one day wipe out all organic life and take over Earth. That day has arrived! The impossible has happened, and Ultron rules the planet! As the few super-hero survivors who remain try desperately to stay alive, Luke Cage learns the staggering secret of Ultron's victory. And when a near-broken Captain America leads a ragtag counterattack, Wolverine makes a controversial and desperate decision - one that creates a new Marvel Universe, and inadvertently brings horrific disaster with it! With one final chance, can the heroes fix everything and defeat Ultron? Collecting AGE OF ULTRON #1-10 and #10AI, AVENGERS ASSEMBLE #14AU-15AU, FANTASTIC FOUR (2012) #5AU, FEARLESS DEFENDERS #4AU, SUPERIOR SPIDER-MAN #6AU, ULTRON #1AU, UNCANNY AVENGERS #8AU, and WOLVERINE & THE X-MEN #27AU.
name: HC

description: The world has fallen to the Rot! Animal Man forms an uneasy alliance with Swamp Thing as the world falls deep into decay. The two heroes travel the decimated planet, scrounging up misfit crimefighters, whose appearances and histories have been changed by this new hell-scape. Will Animal Man and Swamp Thing be able to stop the forces of the Rot and change the world back to what it was? Find out in these tales from ANIMAL MAN #12-17 and SWAMP THING #12 and 17-18.
name: Volume 3

volume.name: Animal Man: Rotworld - The Red Kingdom

description: BATMAN: LEGENDS OF THE DARK KNIGHT presents the new, original adventures of Batman from the acclaimed digital-first series by an all-star lineup of comics' finest talents including Damon Lindelof (Lost, Prometheus), Steve Niles (30 Days of Night), Jeff Lemire (ANIMAL MAN) and more! Discover startling sides of The Dark Knight that span from his earliest days in the cowl to his never-ending battles against Gotham's greatest enemies, including the Joker and Two-Face. Collecting issues #1-5 of BATMAN: LEGENDS OF THE DARK KNIGHT!
name: Volume 1

volume.name: Batman: Legends Of The Dark Knight

description: The new Human Rocket returns! Sam Alexander is a kid bound by the gravity of a small town - and a father whose ridiculous, drunken fairy tales about a 'Nova Corps' were just another heavy burden. But lucky for Sam, gravity soon won't even matter - and those troubles will be a billion miles away. It's a boy, a helmet and an intergalactic legacy! As Sam trains with the Guardians of Galaxy's Gamora and Rocket Raccoon, the helmet leads Nova into intergalactic conflict that will affect the entire Marvel Universe! Mysteries are revealed in this breathtaking new series by the best-selling, award-winning team of Jeph Loeb and Ed McGuinness (HULK, AVENGERS: X-SANCTION)! Collecting NOVA (2013) #1-5 and material from MARVEL NOW! POINT ONE #1.
name: Volume 1

description: This Digital Exclusive features OVER 100 PAGES of Dilton's wackiest creations! Dilton Doiley, Riverdale's resident nutty professor, has a new invention for you! Are you brave enough to see what is? Put on your labcoat and check out over 100 pages of Dilton's craziest scientific experiments. Whether it's a new robot, a time machine, or even a brain-switcher, if it's Dilton's invention, it's definitely doofy!

Lace up those hi-tops and get out on the court- it's time for Arch Madness! This 100 page digital exclusive spotlights some of Archie's highest-scoring basketball stories! Archie, Betty, Jughead and even Dilton are getting in on the game! Featuring over 15 stories with artwork from legendary artists like Stan Goldberg, Fernando Ruiz, and Dan DeCarlo Jr. You can't lose!

Riverdale's resident braniac stars in his own 4-part miniseries, available ONLY on the Archie App! Dilton Doiley has always felt a bit out-of-place at Riverdale High, where people have trouble seeing past his high IQ. So when Brainard University offers him a spot in their prestigious school, Dilton has a big decision to make! Will Archie and the gang be able to convince him to stay at Riverdale High, or is Dilton Doiley college-bound?
name: Drop Out! Part One

description:
Archie imagines what it would be like if he were a private eye, donning the fedora of Detective Sam Scooper! When socialite Veronica Lodge is robbed for the third time in one month, she believes it's an inside job and calls on Scooper to find out which of her mansion staff has been snagging her swag! But the mystery of the missing mansion merch won't be a mystery for long! Find out who's the thief in 'The Ocelot Caper,' the lead story in this fun-filled double digest!

Note: The digital edition (9/11/2013) for this volume was released before the print edition (9/18/2013).
name: I Call My Fantasy... "The Ocelot Caper"
An Experiment In Delicious (A Strange Delivery Interlude); Strange Delivery Part Three

description: Mixed Martial Arts and Hollywood superstar RAMPAGE JACKSON makes his comic book debut in this action packed one-shot from Lion Forge Comics! When an electrified madman tries to force his ex-girlfriend into marriage by threatening her familys lives, the woman turns to Rampage for help. The STREET SOLDIER known as Rampage must overcome this ruthless master of electricity or his first super powered adventure may very well be his last!

character_credits.name: The Man In The Iron Mask

first_appearance_characters.name: The Man In The Iron Mask

description: Wolverine and Osen seek out the leader of the First Clan, hoping the most traditional members of the Hand will help them put an end to Sabretooth's machinations. Will Logan and his old enemies be able to put aside their differences to fight a mutual foe? Or will their history prove too explosive?
name: Hell's Howling Winds

description: Meet the Hellionsa team of misfit Ame-Comi Girls out to have fun and save the world. Its not easy for Black Flash being the only undead, crime-fighting teenager in school. But when she meets Red Raven and her badass besties, she may have finally found a place to fit in.
name: The Teen Hellions

description: Find out How the legend begins! Issue one tells the tale of a young teen named WILLIAM POWER and his epic journey that will cast him at odds with everything he knows! See how this modest teen football captain has the universe turned upside-down and his fate sealed to become the legendary WILL POWER!

person_credits.name: Vince White
person_credits.role: writer, artist, penciler, letterer, inker, cover, production

description: Freshly awaken from a 30 year slumber in stasis, young William Power finds there are those that want him dead or alive, including a blood thirsty mercenary that goes by the name "PAYDAY!"

person_credits.name: Vince White
person_credits.role: writer, artist, penciler, letterer, inker, cover, production

description: Still seeking evidence of his long lost father, Will Power journeys to the Antarctic to find one of his father's forgotten secret labs. In route, Will Power comes face to face with a strange new teenage super team called THE ACTION PACK!

person_credits.name: Vince White
person_credits.role: writer, artist, penciler, letterer, inker, cover, production

description: Will Power is collected by a federal covert ops team called OCTOBER which is led by a man name Commander Fame, who begins to tell William all the government knows about Will's father and the true reason for his building of the Matter Density Converter.

person_credits.name: Vince White
person_credits.role: writer, artist, penciler, letterer, inker, colorist, cover, production

description:
WIth EXCLUSIVE DIGITAL CONTENT including original art and sketches!

There's a dinosaur from the Hollow Earth loose in the Weir, and she's eating Farmer McGregor's sheep!

Can Alice and Frankenstein's Monster stop her - before an irate McGregor puts this purple T-rex down for good?!
name: What Lies Beneath the Badger's House

description:
With a school full of children and a wandering fungal menace on the loose, no one is safe from the fertile fear of Formula X! The second issue of "Beware ..." takes you back to the horrors of high school as a student's experiment grows beyond its innocent intent. A team of three have until midnight to solve the mystery and save the rest of Haven Hallows from ... infection!

This latest offering from the Perkins Bros. is another adventure in neo-retro sci-fi as the next scientific scare plagues unlucky town of Haven Hallows.
As the friends each reflect on their destinies, one finds a secret about her past that is more than she can handle.
name: No One Knows But Me

description: Byron is potentially drugged, hiding in the back room of a wicked bar, with a christian dominatrix, pursued by a horde of Tiki Zombies, led by a possessed Bartender. So what else is new? Written and illustrated by Karl Christian Krumpholz.
Teacher Charlie Wormwood has a photographic memory...and when one of his pupils realizes this, he makes Charlie an irresistible offer.
Antimony and Ysengrin meet with Coyote and learn of his greatest secret.
name: The Great Secret

description: The stakes have never been higher, as Huck escapes the clutches of the C'thulu Queen, is hunted by the deadly Cheshire Cat, and gains a couple of companions along the way.
